需要制定 dataZoom 的 index

``` js
lineChart.dispatchAction({
  type: 'dataZoom',
  dataZoomIndex: 0,
  start: 87.67123287671232,
  end: 100
});
```

另外折线图中建议 [toolbox.feature.dataZoom.yAxisIndex](http://localhost/echarts-doc/test/option.html#toolbox.feature.dataZoom.yAxisIndex) 设为 null，不然框选也会过滤 Y 轴的数据

You can use formatter to add custom text in label.

``` js
xAxis: {
  axisLabl: {
    formatter: function (timestamp) { return ''; }
  }
}
```

